  body

    .container

      h2.form-signin-heading What's the homework??
      //-a little explanatory paragraph. You will obviously want to change your email here.
      //-I want other students to be able to take advantage of this site, so I added the option for students to email me and add another teacher.
      p It's 2015, and the unofficial standard is for teachers to put their homework on their website. Unfortunately, some teachers do not. So my goal here is to maintain up-to-date homework for classes that don't have the homework online. If you have a class that doesn't have the homework online, #[a(href="mailto:me@example.com") email me] and it can be added to this site. You will get a password to add/edit assignments. It is very easy and can be done on your phone in class, so let me know if you'd like to do this for another class.
      br

      p Pick your teacher
      //-create a button link for every teacher in the homeworks folder
      -for (var i=0; i<teachers.length; i++)
        a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-block(href="/#{teachers[i]}") #{teachers[i].charAt(0).toUpperCase() + teachers[i].slice(1)}


